                                <span class="section-heading-lower">estamos para complacerte</span>
                            </h2>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled list-hours mb-5 mx-auto">
                                <li class="list-unstyled-item list-hours-item d-flex">
                                    Domingo
                                    <span class="ms-auto">Cerrado</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="list-unstyled-item list-hours-item d-flex">
                                    Lunes
